                <note rend="inline" type="source">868.51 Public Works/22: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Greece</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Skinner</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Athens</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-02-14T11:00:00+02:00"
                            >February 14, 1929—11 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received February 14—9:05 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>16. At an early hour this morning the Chamber voted ratification of Seligman loan
                    contract which now awaits only favorable action of International Financial
                    Commission in order to become operative.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Skinner</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
